<paragraph blockId="20.[189,1398,1378,1440]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">The upper palatal lamella which does not or hardly reaches the peristome and the non-thickened, knobless peristome are the features that distinguish this subspecies from the nominate subspecies.</paragraph>
